QDM68 is a Q3 DeFRaG demo manager that allow you to :
- Delete, move or copy your worst (or best) demos
- See informations about your demos (Players, rules)
- Check and modify rules
- See some statistics about your demos
- Play a demo

Note : You can add (or delete) new rules by modifying the 
configuration  file 'QDM68.ini'.
On windows it is situated in the QDM68 folder.
On Linux it is situated $HOME/.Config/QDM68 folder.

